T02TD2401E:26b-1: pra kri ti siddhi n'a ma /
T02TD2401E:26b-3: rang bzhin grub pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2401E:26b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2401E:26b-5: mdor bsdus pa yi rim pa ni //
T02TD2401E:26b-6: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin te //
T02TD2401E:26b-7: lus la gnas pa'i blo ldan rnams //
T02TD2401E:26b-8: rjes su dran zhing nyams su blangs //
T02TD2401E:26b-9: yab yum sbyor ba'i nga rgyal bya //
T02TD2401E:26b-10: gang zhig rgyud de'i rdzogs pa'i rim //
T02TD2401E:26b-11: de phyir bdag nyid yi dam gyi //
T02TD2401E:26b-12: nga rgyal dang ni bral mi bya //
T02TD2401E:26b-13: yum ni rigs kyi lha mo ste //
T02TD2401E:26b-14: dpal ldan yab ni dag pa'o //
T02TD2401E:26b-15: de dag gnyis kyi longs spyod ni //
T02TD2401E:26b-17: zhes sdang rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
T02TD2401E:26b-18: gti mug dra ba rnam snang po //
T02TD2401E:26b-19: nga rgyal rin chen 'byung ldan no //
T02TD2401E:26b-20: phrag dog don yod grub pa'o //
T02TD2401E:26b-21: gzhan yang thabs dang shes rab kyi //
T02TD2401E:26b-22: lus la gnas pa 'di dag go //
T02TD2401E:27a-0: sa yi khams ni sangs rgyas spyan @27a * //
T02TD2401E:27a-1: chu khams m'a ma k'i zhes bya //
T02TD2401E:27a-2: gos dkar mo ni me khams te //
T02TD2401E:27a-3: sgrol ma rlung khams ngo bo nyid //
T02TD2401E:27a-4: nam mkha' rdo rje dbang phyug ma //
T02TD2401E:27a-5: sa yi snying po mig dag la //
T02TD2401E:27a-6: phyag na rdo rje rna ba la //
T02TD2401E:27a-7: sna la nam mkha'i snying po ste //
T02TD2401E:27a-8: lce ni spyan ras gzigs dbang po /
T02TD2401E:27a-9: lus la sgrib pa rnam sel te //
T02TD2401E:27a-10: yid la kun du bzang po'o //
T02TD2401E:27a-12: de phyir bdag ni chos dbyings so //
T02TD2401E:27a-13: sa dang me dang rlung khams sogs //
T02TD2401E:27a-14: brjod bya tsam du rnam par sprul //
T02TD2401E:27a-15: rang bzhin dri ma dag pa yi //
T02TD2401E:27a-16: de nas sngags gsum brjod byas nas //
T02TD2401E:27a-17: rang lus khong stong bsam byas nas //
T02TD2401E:27a-18: de dbus bhum las gzhal yas khang //
T02TD2401E:27a-19: sor bzhi tsam gyi rnam par bskyed //
T02TD2401E:27a-20: aom a'a: h'um brjod yi dam lha //
T02TD2401E:27a-21: rnal 'byor dag ni sgo lnga nas //
T02TD2401E:27a-22: gzhal yas dbus su spyan drang bya //
T02TD2401E:27a-23: de nyid thig le zhu byas nas //
T02TD2401E:27a-24: lam du rgyu zhing chos 'byung dbus //
T02TD2401E:27a-25: bril [*zil?] ba lta bu'i thig le la //
T02TD2401E:27a-26: bde gshegs dgug gzhug gnyis med bsam //
T02TD2401E:27a-27: de nas byang chub sems nyid ni //
T02TD2401E:27a-28: padma'i dbyibs ldan bsam byas nas //
T02TD2401E:27a-29: de la bdag nyid sems gtad do //
T02TD2401E:27a-30: rang bzhin grub pa'i thabs zhes bya ba slob dpon rdo ka ris mdzad pa rdzogs so//
